              <li>{#link|Integers#}</li>
              <li>{#link|Floats#}</li>
            </ul>
          </td>
          <td>
            <ul>
              <li>Can cause {#link|overflow|Default Operations#} for integers.</li>
              <li>Invokes {#link|Peer Type Resolution#} for the operands.</li>
              <li>See also {#link|@mulWithOverflow#}.</li>
