      <p>
      {#link|Enum Literals#} can be useful to use with {#syntax#}switch{#endsyntax#} to avoid
      repetitively specifying {#link|enum#} or {#link|union#} types:
      </p>
      {#code_begin|test|test_exhaustive_switch#}
