      {#header_open|Type Coercion: Error Unions#}
      <p>The payload type of an {#link|Error Union Type#} as well as the {#link|Error Set Type#}
      coerce to the error union type:
      </p>
      {#code_begin|test|test_coerce_to_error_union#}
